seller.description: I have worked in various capacities within the design world for the past decade. With a degree in Communications from Azusa Pacific University and a degree in Graphic Design from F.I.D.M., I specialize in logo design, digital marketing, and photography. I appreciate the simple things in life like drinking coffee, listening to music, touring museums, being in nature and cooking a great meal. I’m an advocate for healthy living and am doing my part to make the world a better, cleaner and happier place!

reviews.comment: Arlie W, Did a real good job, took the assignment, redesign of a new logo, real good, immediately made a mockup of 3 logo's already it was hard to choose between them they were all already very good! Took a vote, here in and chose one, after a few minor revisions, everything was very good, delivered a complete package, full of logo's all ready to be used on the website, social media etc. I defiantly recommend Arlie W !

Studioawest is very professional, skilled, and efficient. Create exatly what i want. I am 100% satisfied with my order and would recommend this seller a thousand times. If I could give more than 5 stars to this seller, I would. This is probably the best experience I've ever had on Fiver!.

Once I learned how to best communicate with Arlie things went GREAT! 

She is a detail person so the more specific details that you can provide, the better job she'll do for you. 

We are THRILLED with our logo. It is beyond our expectations and will provide us with a number of unique elements that we can use in our branding efforts for years to come. All who have seen it LOVE it and the cost was VERY fair and reasonable.

We are coffee roasters and in an industry known for text logos and odd names, we wanted something that would be memorable and stand out, and Arlie delivered!  Many thanks!

In the end I’m happy with what I received, but it took a while to get to it. At times I felt like she was not reading my revisions request thoroughly. I’d ask for one thing and she would do something totally different. She is 
The project turned out nicely, but it took a lot of patience and frustration to get there.

Arlie is great at executing the design. 
I was hoping for more design input however. If you know exactly what you want to see, but don't have the technical skill to create the file, this gig is a perfect fit for you. If you're looking for design direction, feedback or suggestions on creating an aesthetically pleasing logo that speaks to your target market, this might not be the answer.
